Bridging the Urban-Rural Divide in Chronic Disease Through Community Engagement 
in Health Program Delivery.

Carter-Edwards L(1), Taylor MM(2).

Author information:
(1)Assistant dean for community engagement and faculty of Health Systems 
Science, Kaiser Permanente Bernard J. Tyson School of Medicine, Pasadena, 
