Cost-effectiveness of prophylactic cranial irradiation in stage III non-small 
cell lung cancer.

Witlox WJA(1), Ramaekers BLT(2), Lacas B(3), Le Pechoux C(4), Sun A(5), Wang 
SY(6), Hu C(7), Redman M(8), van der Noort V(9), Li N(10), Guckenberger M(11), 
