Assessing the Cost-Utility of Universal Hepatitis B Vaccination Among Adults.

Hall EW(1)(2), Weng MK(3), Harris AM(3), Schillie S(4), Nelson NP(3), 
Ortega-Sanchez IR(4), Rosenthal E(5), Sullivan PS(2), Lopman B(2), Jones J(2), 
Bradley H(6), Rosenberg ES(5)(7).

Author information:
(1)School of Public Health, Oregon Health and Science University, Portland, 
Oregon, USA.
(2)Emory University, Rollins School of Public Health, Department of 
